方「一般不會考慮進口貂鼠作為私人寵物飼養的申請。</blockquote><br />\nGoogle 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f509e0fb9230321b071752167a2f932a1b8ade","tid":846414,"uid":204752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"之前想帶隻貓番香港 從正途既話 動物進口有一系列程序要搞 詳情你自己上漁農處睇下要點搞啦 始終唔同動物又唔一樣 你方便既話可以打去問 之前個接線哥哥好好 佢整理埋我需要既file email比我"},{"pid":"5112c943f2cd95e2665fc6f74d769190d050c6df","tid":846414,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"留學都唔建議養寵物<br />\n不如等自己安定咗先養啦<br />\n無謂累咗隻小動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b164c02bb59d2815e2eeb2985babcbe448b8d6c","tid":846414,"uid":167148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f7ad71dbe7b408fa9551f5ce21dab8e021c56e","tid":846414,"uid":200034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"想睇貂鼠圖多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/180610_916796c71451540bbd58c8d8d5db835b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F180610_916796c71451540bbd58c8d8d5db835b.png&h=6d8db8e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/180612_ed7e36fbc6add37a5cc749f437fe1616.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F180612_ed7e36fbc6add37a5cc749f437fe1616.png&h=460340eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f23c64d2ab40f5681b9b5f3aa6274fe86e5ea16c","tid":846414,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b164c02bb59d2815e2eeb2985babcbe448b8d6c","tid":846414,"uid":167148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f7ad71dbe7b408fa9551f5ce21dab8e021c56e","tid":846414,"uid":200034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2